This repository contains precomputed mathematical cache data and/or cache
registry metadata (the "Data"), generated by the Xcelerator Toolkit
(https://github.com/TeamXcelerator/xcelerator-toolkit). The Data may include
high-precision numerical tables, matrices, eigenpairs, spectra, roots,
diagnostics, certificates, manifests, and related metadata.

Permission is granted to persons who lawfully obtain access to this
repository to:

- Download and use the Data to accelerate reproduction of published
  Team Xcelerator findings or for academic research that cites this work
  and the associated publications
- Read, verify, and study the Data for educational purposes
- Cite this repository in academic publications with proper attribution

Permission is NOT granted to:

- Redistribute the Data as part of another dataset or product without
  explicit written permission
- Use the Data or anything derived from it for commercial purposes

The Data are provided "as is", without warranty of any kind. Consumers
should validate every artifact with the Xcelerator Toolkit and must not
assume that any file is correct merely because it is present in a cache
repository.

